{"id":282,"parent_id":266,"book_id":2,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":282,"title":"Revelation 16","subtitle":"","short_title":"Rev.","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/16","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 16"],[".studySummary",["i","God pours out plagues upon the wicked—The nations assemble for Armageddon—Christ comes, islands flee, and mountains cease."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/16.1","order":"03.29.016.28079"},["b","1"],"And I heard a great voice out of the temple saying to the seven angels, Go your ways, and pour out the vials of the wrath of God upon the earth."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/16.2","order":"03.29.016.28080"},["b","2"],"And the first went, and poured out his vial upon the earth; and there fell a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"noisome"],"and grievous sore upon the men which had the mark of the beast, and",["i","upon"],"them which worshipped his image."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/16.3","order":"03.29.016.28081"},["b","3"],"And the second angel poured out his vial upon the sea; and it became as the blood of a dead",["i","man:"],"and every living soul died in the sea."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/16.4","order":"03.29.016.28082"},["b","4"],"And the third angel poured out his vial upon the rivers and fountains of waters; and they became blood."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/16.5","order":"03.29.016.28083"},["b","5"],"And I heard the angel of the waters say, Thou art righteous, O Lord, which art, and wast, and shalt be, because thou hast",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"judged"],"thus."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/16.6","order":"03.29.016.28084"},["b","6"],"For they have",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"shed"],"the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_6b"},"blood"],"of saints and prophets, and thou hast given them blood to drink; for they are",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_6c"},"worthy"],"."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/16.7","order":"03.29.016.28085"},["b","7"],"And I heard another out of the altar say, Even so, Lord God Almighty, true and righteous",["i","are"],"thy judgments."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/16.8","order":"03.29.016.28086"},["b","8"],"And the fourth angel poured out his vial upon the sun; and power was given unto him to scorch men with fire."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/16.9","order":"03.29.016.28087"},["b","9"],"And men were scorched with great heat, and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"blasphemed"],"the name of God, which hath power over these plagues: and they repented not to give him glory."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/16.10","order":"03.29.016.28088"},["b","10"],"And the fifth angel poured out his vial upon the seat of the beast; and his kingdom was full of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"darkness"],"; and they gnawed their tongues for pain,"],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/16.11","order":"03.29.016.28089"},["b","11"],"And blasphemed the God of heaven because of their",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"pains"],"and their sores, and repented not of their deeds."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/16.12","order":"03.29.016.28090"},["b","12"],"And the sixth angel poured out his vial upon the great river Euphrates; and the water thereof was dried up, that the way of the kings of the east might be prepared."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/16.13","order":"03.29.016.28091"},["b","13"],"And I saw three unclean spirits like frogs",["i","come"],"out of the mouth of the dragon, and out of the mouth of the beast, and out of the mouth of the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"false prophet"],"."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/16.14","order":"03.29.016.28092"},["b","14"],"For they are the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"spirits"],"of",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_14b"},"devils"],", working",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_14c"},"miracles"],",",["i","which"],"go forth unto the kings of the earth and of the whole world, to gather them to the",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_14d"},"battle"],"of that great day of God Almighty."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/16.15","order":"03.29.016.28093"},["b","15"],"Behold, I come as a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"thief"],". Blessed",["i","is"],"he that",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_15b"},"watcheth"],", and keepeth his garments, lest he walk naked, and they see his shame."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/16.16","order":"03.29.016.28094"},["b","16"],"And he gathered them together into a place called in the Hebrew tongue",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"Armageddon"],"."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/16.17","order":"03.29.016.28095"},["b","17"],"And the seventh angel poured out his vial into the air; and there came a great voice out of the temple of heaven, from the throne, saying, It is done."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/16.18","order":"03.29.016.28096"},["b","18"],"And there were voices, and thunders, and lightnings; and there was a great",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},"earthquake"],", such as was not since men were upon the earth, so mighty an earthquake,",["i","and"],"so great."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/16.19","order":"03.29.016.28097"},["b","19"],"And the great city was divided into three parts, and the cities of the nations fell: and great",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_19a"},"Babylon"],"came in remembrance before God, to give unto her the cup of the wine of the fierceness of his",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_19b"},"wrath"],"."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/16.20","order":"03.29.016.28098"},["b","20"],"And every island fled away, and the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_20a"},"mountains"],"were not found."],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/16.21","order":"03.29.016.28099"},["b","21"],"And there fell upon men a great",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_21a"},"hail"],"out of heaven,",["i","every stone"],"about the weight of a talent: and men blasphemed God because of the plague of the hail; for the plague thereof was exceeding great."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/16.2a","order":"03.29.016.28100"},["b","2a"],["span.small","GR"],"bad, evil."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/16.5a","order":"03.29.016.28102"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-judge"},"TG Jesus Christ, Judge"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/16.6a","order":"03.29.016.28104"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/prophets-rejection-of"},"TG Prophets, Rejection of"],"."],["div",{"id":"6b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/16.6b","order":"03.29.016.28106"},["b","6b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/martyrdom"},"TG Martyrdom"],"."],["div",{"id":"6c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/16.6c","order":"03.29.016.28108"},["b","6c"],["span.small","GR"],"deserving."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/16.9a","order":"03.29.016.28110"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/blaspheme"},"TG Blaspheme"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/16.10a","order":"03.29.016.28112"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/darkness-spiritual"},"TG Darkness, Spiritual"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/16.11a","order":"03.29.016.28114"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/pain"},"TG Pain"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/16.13a","order":"03.29.016.28116"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/antichrist"},"TG Antichrist"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/false-prophets"},"False Prophets"],"."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/16.14a","order":"03.29.016.28118"},["b","14a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/50.1"},"D&C 50:1"],"."],["div",{"id":"14b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/16.14b","order":"03.29.016.28120"},["b","14b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/24.24"},"Matt. 24:24"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/9.9.8-12"},"2 Ne. 9:9 (8–12)"],"."],["div",{"id":"14c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/16.14c","order":"03.29.016.28122"},["b","14c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/miracle"},"TG Miracle"],"."],["div",{"id":"14d","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/16.14d","order":"03.29.016.28124"},["b","14d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rev/17.14"},"Rev. 17:14"],"."],["div",{"id":"15a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/16.15a","order":"03.29.016.28126"},["b","15a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/luke/21.35"},"Luke 21:35"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rev/3.3"},"Rev. 3:3"],"."],["div",{"id":"15b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/16.15b","order":"03.29.016.28128"},["b","15b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/49.7.5-9"},"D&C 49:7 (5–9)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/106.5.4-5"},"106:5 (4–5)"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/watch"},"TG Watch"],"."],["div",{"id":"16a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/16.16a","order":"03.29.016.28130"},["b","16a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/38.16.15-16"},"Ezek. 38:16 (15–16)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/joel/3.14.9-14"},"Joel 3:14 (9–14)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/zech/14.2.2-5"},"Zech. 14:2 (2–5)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/luke/21.20.20-24"},"Luke 21:20 (20–24)"],"."],["div",{"id":"18a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/16.18a","order":"03.29.016.28132"},["b","18a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/dan/12.1"},"Dan. 12:1"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rev/6.12"},"Rev. 6:12"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rev/11.13.13-14"},"11:13 (13–14)"],"."],["div",{"id":"19a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/16.19a","order":"03.29.016.28134"},["b","19a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/babylon"},"TG Babylon"],"."],["div",{"id":"19b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/16.19b","order":"03.29.016.28136"},["b","19b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-indignation-of"},"TG God, Indignation of"],"."],["div",{"id":"20a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/16.20a","order":"03.29.016.28138"},["b","20a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/64.1"},"Isa. 64:1"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rev/6.14.12-17"},"Rev. 6:14 (12–17)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/133.22.1-42"},"D&C 133:22 (1–42)"],"."],["div",{"id":"21a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/rev/16.21a","order":"03.29.016.28140"},["b","21a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/9.18.13-35"},"Ex. 9:18 (13–35)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/josh/10.11"},"Josh. 10:11"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/13.13"},"Ezek. 13:13"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/38.22"},"38:22"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rev/11.19"},"Rev. 11:19"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/12.6"},"Mosiah 12:6"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/29.16"},"D&C 29:16"],"."]]}
